## Adding a New Exercise Type вАФ Checklist

New exercise types live in `shared/` so they are immediately available for
every CEFR level.

1. Add interface + type to [src/content/shared/types.ts](mdc:src/content/shared/types.ts)
   (the legacy alias `@/content/types` still works вАФ it re-exports from `shared/`)
2. Create component in `src/components/exercises/`
3. Add `case` in [src/components/exercises/ExerciseRenderer.tsx](mdc:src/components/exercises/ExerciseRenderer.tsx)
4. Add template to [src/content/shared/EXERCISE_TEMPLATES.ts](mdc:src/content/shared/EXERCISE_TEMPLATES.ts)
5. Add type to the category list in this rule
